{"tid":1649831,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"冷處理","createTime":"2019-10-12T18:39:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T19:02:02.000Z","uid":305350,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"27b542467013f4e28ef2278d3dad21f18b6b1b51","tid":1649831,"uid":305350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:39:51.000Z","msg":"唔係左膠<br />\n<br />\n我都明白大家好嬲，我都好嬲。<br />\n但因為一個蛋糕而嘈到咁勁，<br />\n係唔係唔記得左真正既敵人喺邊度？<br />\n係邊一班人令到太子站變成靈堂？<br />\n係邊一班人令到食蛋糕都要比人吊？<br />\n<br />\n請大家集中返去主線<br />\n<br />\n致當事人 &amp; Team，<br />\n無論蛋糕係喺你唔知情之下出現又好，你主動提出都好，你同你team任何一個人都可以即時阻止，希望你地真係意識到問題喺邊度。<br />\n<br />\n以下開放宣傳行動及日程表"},{"pid":"3f665a75889028376005d6b4eb53e7d095aabd40","tid":1649831,"uid":305350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:40:05.000Z","msg":"聽日有咩要做呀？"},{"pid":"5a7971db4ebcf4f49ba6bd3bbe8845f651b99dba","tid":1649831,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:40:19.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n[品蔥建議] [拋磚引玉] 如何偽裝成一名合格的&ldquo;愛國港人&rdquo;（藍絲）？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648664\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1648664</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0be972a1c5b13d7c41e558a53d725bc9f7ddec01","tid":1649831,"uid":305350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:40:51.000Z","msg":"我訓唔著呀"},{"pid":"484268eafcd52c283df948b10b94b4cd23061491","tid":1649831,"uid":305350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:41:02.000Z","msg":"大家係唔係咁早訓晒呀？"},{"pid":"003042e3bd12c2d15650af4d06ebc869f76baa1c","tid":1649831,"uid":305350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:41:28.000Z","msg":"做緊文宣呀"},{"pid":"0373de42c22ea63f6ed935d730ddea0d659c4d14","tid":1649831,"uid":305350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:41:38.000Z","msg":"人呢"},{"pid":"bb6e0550d60559491c93a679f3a3169f3bd6e9e6","tid":1649831,"uid":305350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl